<h1>AtrocidadesRSS Reader</h1>

<p>Welcome to the AtrocidadesRSS Reader - a decentralized database of Brazilian historical crimes.</p>

<p>Use the navigation menu to:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Sync</strong> - Download and synchronize database snapshots via torrent</li>
    <li><strong>Search</strong> - Search historical cases by various criteria</li>
    <li><strong>Cases</strong> - Browse and view individual cases</li>
</ul>
